Defaults:
    Server IP:
    Server PORT: 8080

    NLP PORT: 8080
    IMC PORT: 8081

request_type {IMC=0, FACE, DIG, ASR, POS, NER, CHK, SRL, PT0, VBS, SIZE_OF_ENUM};

Communication Protocol:
Client should execute the following in specific order
1. Connect to the server
2. Send request type as enum/int (refer to src/thread.h)
3. Send the size of the input feature, 
this should agree with the input dim of the first layer in the config file
4. Enter the main loop
  4.1 Send feature vector
  4.2 Wait for inference to finish
  4.3 Receive the result
5. Close the socket if the application is done using the service. 
                        
